Simply plug unit into standard electrical outlet and plug appliance into provided receptacle. Appliance can be activated and de-activated by depressing air button, which can be mounted up to 15 feet away. You'll be able to appreciate both the beauty and performance of this item for years to come thanks to superior quality finishing and solid construction....
